 
<p>
Small private jets emit over
<a href="https://www.commondreams.org/news/private-jet-industry">10 times as much</a>
pollution per passenger 
as commercial flights, yet they receive an indirect public subsidy.
<p>
This calls for a big increases in taxes on owning and using those
jets.  It would be just a start at ending the rich people's class war,
but starting would be good.

<p>
 